## 🏆 The World's Largest MCP Skills Collection

65+ production-grade Model Context Protocol servers designed for AI IDEs:

### 🎯 Four Major Categories
- **基础工具 (Basic)** - 15+ 通用处理工具
- **提高工具 (Intermediate)** - 20+ 专业处理工具
- **高级工具 (Advanced)** - 20+ 开发工作流工具
- **特色好玩 (Fun)** - 10+ 娱乐特色工具

### 🚀 Core Skills (Auto-Start)\n- **Git** - Complete version control toolkit\n- **Terminal** - Secure shell execution environment\n- **Code Review** - AI-powered code analysis\n- **Coding Workflow** - Standardized development process\n\n### 🧪 Development Tools\n- **Test Generator** - Automatic test creation\n- **Documentation** - JSDoc & README generation\n- **Code Search** - Advanced semantic search\n- **Code Generator** - Intelligent scaffolding\n- **Dependency Analyzer** - NPM audit & version management\n\n### 🛠️ Language Specific\n- **React Toolkit** - Hooks, components, best practices\n- **TypeScript Master** - Type safety & optimization\n\n### 🔐 DevOps & Security\n- **Docker Toolkit** - Container generation\n- **Security Auditor** - Vulnerability scanning\n- **Performance Optimizer** - Bundle size & speed\n\n### 🔄 Workflows\n- **Debugging Workflow** - Systematic troubleshooting\n- **Refactoring Workflow** - Safe code transformation\n\n---\n\n## Compatibility\n\n✅ **Trae IDE** - Native support\n✅ **Claude Desktop** - Zero configuration\n✅ **Cursor IDE** - Auto-detected\n✅ **Windsurf** - Full MCP support\n✅ **Ollama** - Local model support",
  
